This repository hosts my personal website.

It can be tested using docker:
```
docker run --rm  \
  --volume="//c/Users/arind/Documents/scm/alex-rind.github.com:/srv/jekyll" \
  --volume="//c/Users/arind/Documents/scm/alex-rind.github.com/vendor/bundle:/usr/local/bundle" \
  -p 4000:4000 -it jekyll/jekyll:$JEKYLL_VERSION   jekyll serve --incremental
```
or
```
docker-compose up
```
